<PB REF="00000085.tif" N="69"></L>
<L>Alle godes lawe he fulle&thorn;. &thorn;e newe. and ek &thorn;e olde.</L>
<L N="308">&THORN;at haue&thorn; &thorn;eos ilke two luuen. and wel heom wile atholde.</L>
<L>Ah so&thorn; ich hit eu segge. ofte we agulte&thorn; alle.</L>
<L>For strong hit is to stonde longe. and lyht hit is to falle.</L>
